{"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"A picker allowing to expose several radio buttons and choose only one within the others.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Each radio button contains a “tag”, i.e. a supposed to be unique value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The picker will expose the choosen value through this “tag”.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It has also some configuration elements which will override the one applied to nested ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"text":" (divider, read only and error mode, layout and outlined)","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadioPicker","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"Tag","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":"> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Tag","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SH","text":"Hashable","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom radio trait."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The picker itself does no have any defined accessiiblity value, label or identifier ; it remains in the users hands to define which one will be used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However if defined in the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioPickerData","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" the items inside the picker will have such accessibility identifiers."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Forbidden by design","level":2,"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":" in both an error situation and a read only state."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":" in both an error situation and a disabled state."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":" in both a read only and a disabled state."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Code samples","level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define the elements to display in radio buttons using OUDSRadioPickerData.","    \/\/ This object has the same properties as the OUDSRadioItem,","    \/\/ and some of them are optional withdefault values set","    var someDataToPopulate: [OUDSRadioPickerData<String>] {","        [","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_1\",","                                        label: \"Virgin Holy Lava\",","                                        additionalLabel: \"Very spicy\",","                                        helper: \"No alcohol, only tasty flavors\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"flame\")),","","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_2\",","                                        label: \"IPA beer\",","                                        helper: \"From Brewdog company\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"dog.fill\")),","","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_3\",","                                        label: \"Mineral water\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"waterbottle.fill\")),","        ]","    }","","    \/\/ Prepare the selection, with a value previously selected","    \/\/ Use the data and the binding for the picker.","    @State var selection: String = \"Choice_1\"","","    \/\/ Here the picker is vertical","    OUDSRadioPicker(selection: $selection, radios: someDataToPopulate)","","    \/\/ The picker can apply some settings to all its radio buttons.","    \/\/ It can be also horitzontal with a scroll indicator.","    \/\/ Here all the the radio buttons are in read only mode and use reversed layout.","    OUDSRadioPicker(selection: $selection,","                    radios: someDataToPopulate,","                    isReversed: true,","                    isReadOnly: true,","                    placement: .horitzontal(true))"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","text":"Design documentation","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There is no online specification as this component is not an official OUDSThemesContract one"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Theme rendering","level":2,"anchor":"Theme-rendering"},{"type":"heading","text":"Orange","level":3,"anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineConten